metadata.name: Baby Shark
metadata.description: Great White Shark's Bay is an NFT-collection of 10,000 unique Great White Shark NFTs living on the Ethereum Blockchain. All Sharks are great, but some are rarer than others. Your Shark doubles as your Shark's Bay membership card - the testament of your help for endangered great white sharks and grants access to members-only benefits - the first is private area on the official discord where we do giveaways, activities, and provide sharklists for new upcoming projects to the holders. Future areas and perks can be unlocked by the community through roadmap activation. Together we can save great white shark lives.
